reviewText: the person that I got this DVD for was surprized he didn't know there was a Documentary of Drake

This documentary shows pictures and is being narrated by i don't know who. Drake is not part of this documentary, its just people talking about his talent and what they like about him. Theres many cuts of the film that come from other sources. Definitively not worth the money maybe if it was $7.00. Everything in the film i had already watched, like i said it came from other sources.
